data.description: FABULOUS FIND!! This move in ready property is perfect as starter home or an investment property.  This home offers 3BR/1BA with 1176 square feet of living space. Home  has been well maintained, has newer kitchen cabinets, appliances, paint, and carpet. Refrigerated air, All appliances convey including washer and dryer. This home sits in a very quiet and established neighborhood. Close to EVERYTHING shopping, restaurants, Farmers market downtown, Old Mesilla and NMSU. This home is by APPT ONLY so call me today to make an appt to view this great property before you miss out!!
